      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<ab>
	  (This) pillar (is) the gift of the preacher 
	  <persName key="pers:Svātimitra">Svātimitra</persName>,
	  the son of Nanda (?) (and) the discipline of the sthavira ...
	  of the venerable Dhammutariyas from 
	  <placeName key="pl:Śūrpāraka">Śūrpāraka</placeName>,
	  together with [his father and mother?].
	</ab>
